				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-11/poem-8G2eRSf5t3T7CCZqLVLUlQ">Cảm ngộ kỳ 11 - 感遇其十一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/%C4%90%E1%BB%99c-b%C3%A1o-k%E1%BB%B7-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-AZflaZHWGxQpsZHLeTZ0sg">Độc báo kỷ sự - 讀報紀事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%E1%BB%AF-D%E1%BB%B1c/H%E1%BA%A1-L%C6%B0-ph%C3%A1n-quan-t%E1%BA%B1ng-tr%E1%BA%ADt-ph%E1%BB%A5c-nh%E1%BA%ADm-Nam-S%C3%A1ch-ch%C3%A2u/poem-AKaq3qmtwZ0FF-ZjdWXdWQ">Hạ Lư phán quan tằng trật phục nhậm Nam Sách châu - 賀廬判官增秩復任南策州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nh%E1%BB%AF-D%E1%BB%B1c/author-Gb-Ht5DceR7EDVtjdSr3Zw">Phạm Nhữ Dực</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%B0/K%E1%BB%87/poem-xHz2CleeHEwbHmfpO72KYg">Kệ - 偈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thi%E1%BB%87n-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-%C4%91%E1%BA%A1i-s%C6%B0/author-D3nlI_QzeVjknjQ7vGsW3w">Thiện Đạo đại sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Kh%E1%BA%A3i-Si%C3%AAu/K%E1%BB%B7-s%E1%BB%B1-k%E1%BB%B3-14/poem-q0cR5-0gLnsghj8YwB6Nag">Kỷ sự kỳ 14 - 紀事其十四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Kh%E1%BA%A3i-Si%C3%AAu/author-v6D2LCbIpae0gM4Dq3ytUA">Lương Khải Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/L%E1%BB%99-qu%C3%A1-B%E1%BA%AFc-Ninh-H%E1%BA%A3i-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1-h%E1%BB%AFu-c%E1%BA%A3m-ng%C5%A9-c%E1%BB%95-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-kzcEQT3mDPWAo5nViNxK_A">Lộ quá Bắc Ninh, Hải Dương tức sự hữu cảm ngũ cổ thập lục vận - 路過北寧海陽即事有感五古十六韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-V%C4%83n-Si%C3%AAu/author-t0ibbyX9M2Hpw0m6n5VY-Q">Nguyễn Văn Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/M%E1%BB%B9-Bi-t%C3%A2y-nam-%C4%91%C3%A0i/poem-fAd4MSmwt6gK0B7VvxL7yg">Mỹ Bi tây nam đài - 渼陂西南臺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-C%C6%A1/Ph%C3%A1t-An-Nh%C3%A2n-d%E1%BB%8Bch/poem-CepIVzQjGkZp6TyowXJ8Cg">Phát An Nhân dịch - 發安仁驛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-C%C6%A1/author-oVwYIEYCT983JTs6qs8v3A">Lưu Cơ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thanh-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-gi%C3%A1p/poem-eLwH--2-DDTbNLkdQMTwXQ">Thanh Dương giáp - 青陽峽</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A3-M%C3%A2n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-III/poem-EsyilYBXJVcg5eoS7vsfEA">Vô đề (III) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BA%A3-M%C3%A2n/author-bg2Iw4F0Q1WB-Vf8_0Kqcw">Khả Mân</a>)<br></div>	</div>
